[Student "S"]
{EAST has a tough decision after the two Control-showing bids.

If he uses Blackwood and WEST shows two Aces he will be no better off, because he won't know if one 
of the Aces is the useless \SA. Based on knowing that WEST holds the \DA, 
he bids 6\H, hoping that he can at least make that and that 7 isn't a laydown!}

